3.3.0.name: wordpress/sisow-for-woocommerce
3.3.0.description:
This plug-in contains all the payment methods from Sisow for WooCommerce. The plug-in works on WooCommerce 1.6 and WooCommerce 2.x.

For now this plug-in contains the following payment methods:

  • iDEAL
  • MisterCash
  • SofortBanking
  • CreditCard
  • OverBoeking
  • Ebill
  • Webshop GiftCard
  • Fijn cadeaukaart
  • PayPal
